{"tid":1195074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★廣西高鐵G436疑似被雷擊中：火球爆燃，逼停列車","createTime":"2019-06-09T13:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:29:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"02a1237be2fe3172befa7000da369f67786e3acd","tid":1195074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"IT之家6月9日消息今天上午，由柳州開往武漢的G436次高鐵列車即將駛入全州南站時，遇到突發狀況，6號車廂上方電力引擎疑似遭到雷擊並發生爆炸，導致緊急停車、停電。<br />\n<br />\n據一位目擊者鄒女士稱，她正好在6號車廂，當時看到巨大的火球在眼前窗邊爆開，並感受到車廂震動<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2019/6/20190609_183415_99.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ithome.com%2Fnewsuploadfiles%2F2019%2F6%2F20190609_183415_99.png&h=6d5e53c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事發時間為早上9點，G436次動車正準備進入全州南站，爆炸就發生在6號車廂上方，火球爆燃，一聲巨響過後，火車頓時停滯不前，乘客們受到不小的驚嚇。所幸雷擊事件未對車廂內乘客造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於G436列車的突發狀況，整條線路均受到影響，該趟列車停滯超過兩個小時。在當天中午12時左右，列車恢復行駛並正常開進了全州南站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/0/427/359.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2F0%2F427%2F359.htm&d=sUHHPMw%2FtTWAhlV0Ap%2Bq43wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=ab624b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/0/427/359.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ad103e82d0bf1f97aba4a3f74e91cdaf9a15f6df","tid":1195074,"uid":1643,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"係開心既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecac0efd7a7111eee7a09b8343e4718a0099454f","tid":1195074,"uid":113922,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"d3b311be0d9642968d28a8d86e0dcfb4913c6e74","tid":1195074,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34324ebd6302e952c0958efe51db2897edbd5e3","tid":1195074,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0